values:
Eeeeeh, YATTA!

Saa...don't ask me why I'm in such a good mood. I don't know. But I am. That's what's important, right? Yosh!

OH! I KNOW WHY!

But I'm not telling.

Hee.

:D

*takes a deep breath*

<font size="7">HAPPY BIRTHDAY YUU-CHAN!!!</font>

:D

Atobe-buchou, that was the BEST BIRTHDAY PARTY EVER! :D Though...I think the present fairy might have gotten confused. I don't think I was supposed to get one, too. But I did! And it's the best present I've ever gotten! I adore my new Pillow-san. ^______^ Except...I burned his dinner. ;o; That was really sad. It wound up being a good night, though, so I guess that's what's important, eh? I think I'm going tojmhjynnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnn ((he fell asleep >D))

Saaaa, I had an exciiiiiiiiiiiiting day the other day! I fell asleep on the bus and kind of woke up at Seigaku, but I got to talk (and jog) with Fuji-san! Good luck on your surgery, Fuji-saaaaaaan! I'll be rooting for you!

And and and... I have a new favorite pillow! :D So comfy~

I think I'm going to go take a nap, now. Atobe-buchou has me doing a lot of after school practice 'cause I missed school~
